# SAP IBP (Integrated Business Planning)

> **SAP IBP (Integrated Business Planning)** is SAP's cloud-based Supply Chain Planning solution that helps organizations optimize demand planning, inventory management, supply planning, response planning, and Sales & Operations Planning (S&OP). It enables businesses to make data-driven decisions using real-time analytics and machine learning.

