# Overview

SAP IBP is SAP's next-generation cloud platform for supply chain planning. It replaces many planning capabilities previously available in SAP APO and provides advanced forecasting, inventory optimization, demand sensing, and scenario planning.

Organizations use SAP IBP to:

- Improve demand forecasting
- Optimize inventory levels
- Balance supply and demand
- Improve S&OP processes
- Increase forecast accuracy
- Respond quickly to supply chain disruptions
- Improve collaboration across departments

