# Real-World Example

A global consumer goods company experiences seasonal demand fluctuations.

1. SAP IBP analyzes historical sales data.
2. Machine learning predicts future demand.
3. Supply Planning balances manufacturing capacity.
4. Inventory Optimization recommends stock levels.
5. Procurement orders raw materials.
6. Executives review plans during the monthly S&OP meeting.
7. Supply chain performance is monitored through Control Tower dashboards.

